nodes.text: Keldran was an individual who recommended a security team accompany Kaya Natari, a Czerka Corporation researcher, to the corporation's survey of the ruined Jedi Enclave on the planet Dantooine. The security team saved Natari when creatures attacked Natari at the site, prompting Natari to record a note in a field journal reminding Natari to thank Keldran for recommending the security.
